1. *Muzej* je otvoren svakog dana osim ponedjeljkom. (The *museum* is open every day except on Mondays.)
2. Ovaj *muzej* ima veliku kolekciju umetničkih dela. (This *museum* has a large collection of art pieces.)
3. Prošle nedelje smo posetili *muzej* istorije. (Last week we visited the *museum* of history.)
4. *Muzeju* je potrebna nova oprema za očuvanje artefakata. (*The museum* needs new equipment for preserving artifacts.)
5. Danas idemo u *muzej* nauke i tehnike. (Today we are going to the *museum* of science and technology.)
6. U *muzeju* su otkrili retku sliku jednog od najpoznatijih slikara. (In *the museum* they discovered a rare painting by one of the most famous painters.)
7. Razgledali smo izložbu u novootvorenom *muzeju*. (We toured the exhibition at the newly opened *museum*.)
8. Direktor *muzeja* je najavio veliku renovaciju zgrade. (The director of *the museum* announced a major renovation of the building.)
9. U *muzeju* su organizovali predavanje o antičkoj arhitekturi. (*The museum* organized a lecture on ancient architecture.)
10. Zaposleni u *muzeju* rade na katalogizaciji novih eksponata. (The employees at *the museum* are working on cataloging new exhibits.)